ndex URL, ping Sitemap v\u00e0 \u0111o t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 website c\u0169ng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft khi b\u1ea1n c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt m\u1ed9t ho\u1eb7c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u0169 v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">B\u1ea3o m\u1eadt ch\u1ed1ng hack cho website<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd th\u00ec ngay c\u1ea3 c\u00e1ch x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng domain DNS th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt cho website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Google lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ch\u1ed1ng hack b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1eb1ng email.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Google-Search-Console-thong-bao-site-bi-hacked.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"939\" height=\"482\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Google-Search-Console-thong-bao-site-bi-hacked.png\" alt=\"Google Search Console Thong Bao Site Bi Hacked\" class=\"wp-image-27049\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Google-Search-Console-thong-bao-site-bi-hacked.png 939w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Google-Search-Console-thong-bao-site-bi-hacked-300x154.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Google-Search-Console-thong-bao-site-bi-hacked-700x359.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Google-Search-Console-thong-bao-site-bi-hacked-768x394.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/Google-Search-Console-thong-bao-site-bi-hacked-218x112.png 218w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 939px) 100vw, 939px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Site b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb hack v\u00e0 Google Search Console c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o b\u1ea1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o Google Search Console ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u website b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb hack?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>D\u1ef1a v\u00e0o 3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u sau m\u00e0 Google thu th\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng cho b\u1ea1n:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Spam links<\/strong>. Website b\u1ecb hack s\u1ebd ch\u00e8n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u link r\u00e1c v\u00e0o to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u00e0 website t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 Google s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o cho b\u1ea1n.<\/li><li><strong>Spam keyword<\/strong>. Google lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb kho\u00e1 li\u00ean quan qua n\u1ed9i dung b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u00e0 khi blog b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb hack th\u00ec n\u1ed9i dung b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft &#8220;hack&#8221; s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e8n t\u1eeb kho\u00e1 v\u00f4 t\u1ed9i v\u1ea1 so v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. Google ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n.<\/li><li><strong>Thay \u0111\u1ed5i code<\/strong>. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 HTML l\u00e0 Google c\u00f3 thu th\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0 khi code JS tr\u00ean site b\u1ecb thay \u0111\u1ed5i, \u0111\u0103c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 g\u1eedi email th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 Google b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng cho b\u1ea1n.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng \u1edf vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng, Google s\u1ebd b\u1eadt nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem nh\u01b0 Safe Mode c\u1ee7a tr\u00ecnh duy\u1ec7t k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ngay tr\u00ean trang k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef nh\u01b0 &#8220;this site maybe be hacked&#8221;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/202